          <!-- begin cnt --><p>
	<a id="intro" name="intro"></a></p>
<h2>
	Introduction</h2>
<p>
	Fit a cubic spline to a given data set in a least square sense.</p>
<!-- begin par --><div class="parameters">
	<a id="par" name="par"></a>
	<h2>
		Parameters</h2>
<!-- begin lst -->	<ul>
		<li class="req">
			<span class="reqlabel">ASCII data file containing the pairs (xi, yi) to be fitted</span></li>
		<li class="req">
			<span class="reqlabel">Number of knots defining the spline</span> The default value is 10.</li>
		<li class="req">
			<span class="reqlabel">File to store the obtained knots</span></li>
		<li>
			<span class="label">Maximum iteration number</span> The default value is 500.</li>
		<li>
			<span class="label">Refine given knots</span></li>
		<li>
			<span class="label">Relative decrease in misfit function to declare convergence</span></li>
		<li>
			<span class="label">More verbose output</span></li>
	</ul>
<!-- end lst --></div>
<!-- end par --><!--
