--><p>
	<a id="ref" name="ref"></a></p>
<h2>
	References</h2>
<p>
	R. Biloti, L. T. Santos and M. Tygel. <i>Automatic smoothing by optimal splines</i>, Revista Brasileira da Geof&iacute;sica, 21(2), pp. 173-178, 2005.</p>
<p>
	J. Schleicher and R. Biloti. <i>A frequency criterion for optimal node selection in smoothing with cubic splines</i>, Geophysical Prospecting, 56, pp.229-237, 2008.</p>
